s (Level 3)\n- SQL (Level 3)\n- HTML (Level 3)\n- CSS (Level 3)\n- JavaScript (Level 3)\n\n### **Soft Skills:**\n- Teamwork\n- Communication\n- Time Management\n- Work Ethic\n\nIf you have any questions about how to leverage these skills for job opportunities or further development, feel free to ask! 😊", "timestamp": "2025-12-19T11:44:42.825Z"}, {"id": "ae4b9211-6080-4420-96e6-e5b5ef117854", "role": "user", "content": "Recommend courses - make sure they exist in the system", "timestamp": "2025-12-19T11:45:02.281Z"}, {"id": "ae4b9211-6080-4420-96e6-e5b5ef117854", "role": "assistant", "content": "Absolutely, Litikesh! Here are some recommended courses that align well with your skills and can help you fill any gaps:\n\n### **Recommended Courses:**\n\n1. **Cyber Security** (76% match)\n   - **Type**: Technical\n   - **Why**: With your programming skills, this course will enhance your knowledge in a critical area of demand.\n\n2. **Excel 2016 Essentials** (75% match)\n   - **Type**: Technical\n   - **Why**: Excel skills are essential in many fields, including data analysis and quality assurance.\n\n3. **Access 2016 Essentials** (75% match)\n   - **Type**: Technical\n   - **Why**: Learning Access can help you manage databases effectively, complementing your SQL skills.\n\n### **Additional Courses:**\n- **Delivering Constructive Criticism** (Soft Skill)\n- **Virtual Team Building And Management** (Soft Skill)\n- **Basic Bookkeeping** (Technical)\n\nThese courses can enhance your skill set and make you more competitive in the job market. Would you like to enroll in any of these courses or need more information about them? 📚✨", "timestamp": "2025-12-19T11:45:08.985Z"}]', '2025-12-19 11:44:18.03944+00', '2025-12-19 11:45:08.985+00'),
