omer feedback.\n   - **Skills Gap**: Familiarity with survey tools may be beneficial.\n\n4. **Peer Tutoring Intern**\n   - **Match Score**: 75%\n   - **Why it fits**: Your role as a Class Representative and your teamwork skills make you a good candidate for tutoring.\n   - **Skills Gap**: None identified; great fit!\n\n5. **School Store Ops Intern (Simulation)**\n   - **Match Score**: 60%\n   - **Why it fits**: Your organizational skills and experience in managing school activities will be useful in this role.\n   - **Skills Gap**: None identified; great fit!\n\n### Next Steps:\n- **Apply**: If you haven''t already, consider applying to the Food Safety Intern position as it seems to be the best match.\n- **Skill Development**: You might want to look into courses related to medical coding if you''re interested in that role.\n- **Networking**: Connect with professionals in these fields through platforms like LinkedIn to gain insights and advice.\n\nWould you like more details on any specific job, or do you want to filter by location/type? 😊", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T07:09:53.044Z"}]', '2025-12-23 07:09:35.070654+00', '2025-12-23 07:09:53.044+00'),
