lps you develop confidence in professional settings, improving your communication skills.\n   - **Why This Course?**: Confidence is key in interviews and workplace interactions, making it a valuable addition to your skill set.\n\n### Next Steps:\n- **Enroll in One or More Courses**: Choose the courses that align best with your career goals.\n- **Set a Learning Schedule**: Allocate specific time slots each week to focus on these courses to ensure steady progress.\n\nWould you like help with anything specific regarding these courses or how to manage your learning schedule? 📅✨", "timestamp": "2025-12-26T09:48:38.104Z"}]', '2025-12-26 09:46:44.468521+00', '2025-12-26 09:48:38.104+00'),
