ng your teamwork and communication abilities.\n\n### Step 4: Create an Action Plan\n1. **Short-Term Goals (0-6 months)**:\n   - Apply for internships like the Cyber Safety Ambassador and Peer Tutoring Intern.\n   - Enroll in relevant courses (Cyber Security, Excel Essentials).\n\n2. **Medium-Term Goals (6-12 months)**:\n   - Gain hands-on experience through internships.\n   - Start building a portfolio of projects related to data analysis or quality assurance.\n\n3. **Long-Term Goals (1-3 years)**:\n   - Pursue full-time roles in data science, quality assurance, or cybersecurity.\n   - Consider further education or certifications in your chosen field.\n\n**Next Step:** Would you like to dive deeper into any specific career path or job application strategy? 🚀", "timestamp": "2025-12-19T11:49:00.249Z"}]', '2025-12-19 11:45:52.274494+00', '2025-12-19 11:49:00.249+00'),
