s)\n\n- **Milestones:**\n  - Complete at least 2 courses.\n  - Engage in group activities or discussions to practice teamwork.\n\n#### **Phase 2: Intermediate Skills (3-6 months)**\nOnce you have the basics down, move on to more specialized skills relevant to your desired role.\n\n- **Courses to Consider:**\n  - **Basic Bookkeeping** (0% progress) - if you’re leaning towards administrative roles.\n  - **Delivering Constructive Criticism** (0% progress) - valuable for any workplace.\n\n- **Milestones:**\n  - Complete 2-3 courses and apply skills in practical scenarios, like internships or volunteer work.\n  - Build a resume that highlights your new skills.\n\n#### **Phase 3: Advanced Skills (6-12 months)**\nFocus on advanced skills and specific tools required for your target role.\n\n- **Courses to Consider:**\n  - **Cyber Security** (0% progress) - if interested in tech roles.\n  - **Blockchain Basics** (0% progress) - for roles in tech or finance.\n\n- **Milestones:**\n  - Complete advanced courses.\n  - Work on a project or case study that demonstrates your skills.\n\n### Step 4: Continuous Learning and Networking\n- Join professional networks relevant to your field.\n- Attend workshops or webinars to stay updated on industry trends.\n\n### Next Steps\n1. **Choose a Target Role:** Let me know which role you want to pursue or if you have another in mind.\n2. **Add Skills:** Consider adding any skills you already have to your profile so we can refine your roadmap further.\n3. **Start Courses:** Begin with the courses listed in Phase 1.\n\nWould you like to explore a specific role or skill further? 😊", "timestamp": "2025-12-23T07:28:09.076Z"}]', '2025-12-23 07:27:42.178172+00', '2025-12-23 07:28:09.076+00'),
